tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE differential_expression (
    de_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    gene_id UUID,
    sample_id UUID,
    fold_change FLOAT,
    p_value FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE DifferentiallyExpressedGenes (
    diff_gene_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    gene_id INT,
    fold_change FLOAT,
    p_value FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (gene_id) REFERENCES GeneExpressionData(gene_id)
);

CREATE TABLE GeneExpressionData ( gene_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 expression_value FLOAT,
 sample_id UUID,
 timestamp TIMESTAMP
)
